{"article_id":"36Ucw7ugFaZw7KyG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"If he had been a senator during President Donald Trump 's impeachment trial earlier this year ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"John Bolton says","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"he probably would have voted for a conviction .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"There 's a certain irony in that ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"given that Trump 's former national security adviser , out Tuesday with an explosive new book about his former boss , refused to testify in the House impeachment hearings","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"and then offered to testify in the Senate trial","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"if subpoenaed ;","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"Senate Republicans predictably declined","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"before voting to acquit .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"But on that , as on most things , Bolton is unapologetic about his decisions .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"He is not a man","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"given to second thoughts","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"or particularly worried about provoking the person","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"generally seen as the most powerful in the world , the one","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"who went to court","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"to try to stop publication of the book","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"and seize his proceeds .","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"Witness what happened","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"when his interview with on Thursday was over :","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Bolton stood to pose for a photograph","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"holding a copy of `` The Room","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"Where It Happened , '' the memoir","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"being published by Simon & Schuster .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"`` Shall I hold it like this ? ''","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"he asked with a broad grin ,","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"lifting it over his head .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"He was unmistakably mimicking Trump 's controversial photo op this month","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"when the president held aloft a Bible in front of St. John 's Church","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"after protesters had been cleared from his way in Lafayette Square in Washington .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"It is not revealing classified information to report","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"that relations between the former national security adviser and the president","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"he served","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"have gotten a little rocky .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Bolton :","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Prosecutor firing could be 'consistent ' with what he saw","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"One tantalizing passage in the book suddenly seemed prescient this weekend","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"when the Trump administration fired Geoffrey Berman , the U.S. attorney for the Southern District of New York .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"When Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan complained in December 2018 about the office 's investigation into a Turkish state-owned bank ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Bolton wrote ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"`` Trump then told Erdogan","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"he would take care of things ''","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"once he replaced Southern District prosecutors with `` his people . ''","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"we know at this point ''","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"whether the precipitating event for the firing involved the Turkish bank ,","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"called Halkbank ,","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"or something else ,","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"Bolton said in a brief follow-up interview Sunday .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"But he said","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"`` it could be consistent '' with the president 's attitude toward investigations","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"that he observed","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"when he was in the White House .","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"Pence :","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Bolton says","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"VP was an ally and equally 'stunned ' by some Trump actions","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Trump 's Tulsa rally :","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"He wanted to 'slow the testing down ' and other takeaways","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Four months before the election , Bolton , 71 , is out with a book","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that portrays Trump as incompetent , uninformed , incurious , erratic , enamored with foreign strongmen , obsessed with his reelection","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"and driven solely by self-interest","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"- in a word , unfit to be president .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"`` He 's almost proud of not learning much about the subject matter of national security , ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Bolton said .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"He called working in the Trump White House `` like living inside a pinball machine . ''","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"The president has responded to accounts of Bolton 's book with a volley of insults .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"He told Politico","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"that his former top aide was a `` sick customer '' and someone","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"seen by his White House colleagues as `` totally nuts . ''","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"To Sean Hannity on Fox News , he called Bolton `` a washed-up guy . ''","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"On Twitter , he described `` Wacko John Bolton '' as `` a disgruntled boring fool , ''","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"adding ,","depth":17},{"id":72,"text":"`` What a dope ! '' `","depth":17},{"id":73,"text":"` You know ,","depth":16},{"id":74,"text":"whoever hired Bolton","depth":17},{"id":75,"text":"should get fired , ''","depth":17},{"id":76,"text":"Bolton said dryly .","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"That , of course , would be Trump .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"`` I 've been accused of a lot of things over the course of my career .","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"I 've never been accused of hiding my views .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"So I think","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"he knew what he was getting ''","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"when he named Bolton to one of the most powerful jobs in the White House in April 2018 .","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"He would last for 17 months","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"until Bolton resigned","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"( says Bolton )","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"or Trump fired him","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"( says Trump ) .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"Bolton 's downtown office has evidence of happier times .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"On one wall hangs an oversize print of a Wall Street Journal illustration","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"- a gift from Ivanka Trump -","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that shows Trump , Bolton and Secretary of State Mike Pompeo astride a chess board across from Iranian Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei and President Hassan Rouhani .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"`` To John , ''","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"Trump has written on it with a black Sharpie above his distinctive signature .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"`` Great job ! ''","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"The Trump administration has done more than just talk about the book .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"The Justice Department last week asked a federal judge to halt its publication , a request","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"the judge rejected Saturday .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"`` For reasons","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"that hardly need to be stated ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"the Court will not order nationwide seizure and destruction of a political memoir , ''","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"U.S. District Judge Royce Lamberth wrote .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"The publisher had testified","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"that 200,000 copies of the book had already been shipped ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"and its contents have been reported in news outlets around the world .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"But the judge also said","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Bolton `` likely jeopardized national security ''","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"by including classified material","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"and could be legally liable for failing to complete the pre-publication review process","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"to which he had committed","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"when he received his security clearance .","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"Bolton says","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"the administration ,","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"after initially clearing the book ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"misused the review process","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"to delay publication for political reasons .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"So far , the president 's ferocious reaction seems to be boosting Bolton 's proceeds .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"`` The Room","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Where It Happened , ''","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"which got Bolton an advance","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"reported at $ 2 million ,","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"has shot to No . 1 on Amazon.com .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"Advance sales have made it the top-selling book in the country .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi has also denounced the book ,","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"but not because Bolton makes damaging allegations against the president .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"It 's because he did n't make them sooner .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"`` He chose royalty over patriotism , ''","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"she told reporters ,","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"calling his decision","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"not to testify at the House impeachment hearings","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"`` arrogant . ''","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"That said ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Pelosi noted","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"that several Senate Republicans have said","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Bolton 's account would n't have changed their minds","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"about whether to vote to remove Trump from office .","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"Lawmaker reaction :","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"'Author ,","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"but he ' s no patriot ' :","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"Lawmakers react to Bolton 's new book on Trump","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Bolton now confirms the basics of the Democratic case against Trump on Ukraine .","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"He says","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"the president explicitly tied the release of U.S. military aid to an investigation by Ukraine into his political rivals .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"That allegation persuaded the Democratic-controlled House to impeach the president ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"although the Republican-controlled Senate acquitted him .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"`` I think","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"I probably would have '' voted to convict ,","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"Bolton said ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"`` although , honestly , we still do n't know everything","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"there is to know about Ukraine .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"A lot of conduct can be reprehensible","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"without being impeachable . ''","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"Bolton accuses the House of `` impeachment malpractice ''","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"for not launching a broader and longer investigation , one","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"that might still be going on today .","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"For instance , in an episode reminiscent of Ukraine ,","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"he says ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"Trump solicited election help from China .","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"According to Bolton ,","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"at a summit dinner in Japan last year , Trump asked Chinese President Xi Jinping to increase purchases of American soybeans and wheat","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"to help his reelection prospects in farm states .","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"He was `` pleading with Xi","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"to ensure","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"he 'd win , ''","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"Bolton writes ,","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"to use China 's economic clout for his political benefit .","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"Bolton says","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"he recorded Trump 's exact words","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"but was ordered to delete them from the text during the government 's review process .","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"Bolton 's depiction of Trump behind the scenes ranges from the shocking to the comic .","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"At one point ,","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"Bolton says ,","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"Trump seemed unaware","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"that Great Britain was a nuclear power .","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"( It has been since 1952 . )","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"At another , he asked","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"if Finland was part of Russia .","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"( It 's not . )","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"While books about Trump have become a cottage industry in the publishing world ,","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"Bolton is the highest-ranking former Trump official","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"to depict the president in such a scathing light .","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"He carries the credentials of a conservative","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"who has served in the previous three Republican administrations ,","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"including as U.N. ambassador for President George W. Bush .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"Bolton argues","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"that the electoral damage from his book is more problematic for Trump","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"than his testimony before Congress would have been , and more appropriate .","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"`` Impeachment is the guard rail in the Constitution","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"that 's supposed to be used only in extreme circumstances , ''","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"`` The real guard rail in the Constitution is the election . ''","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"Bolton said","depth":5},{"id":192,"text":"he voted for Trump in 2016","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"but wo n't vote for him in November .","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"Nor will he vote for Joe Biden ,","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"calling the presumptive Democratic candidate and his party unacceptable on national security policy .","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"Instead ,","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":198,"text":"he plans to write in the name of a conservative leader","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"yet to be determined .","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"Bolton packed up his office","depth":5},{"id":201,"text":"and left the White House on Sept. 10 .","depth":5},{"id":202,"text":"A lot has happened since then .","depth":4},{"id":203,"text":"That was a week before the first reports of a whistleblower complaint","depth":6},{"id":204,"text":"that had been filed about Trump 's phone call with the Ukrainian president .","depth":6},{"id":205,"text":"It was two months before China confirmed the first case of the novel coronavirus .","depth":5},{"id":206,"text":"The nationwide wave of protests against police violence and racial injustice would n't begin until this spring .","depth":7},{"id":207,"text":"Trump would n't walk across Lafayette Square ,","depth":8},{"id":208,"text":"cleared of protests ,","depth":9},{"id":209,"text":"and hold aloft a Bible until this month .","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"Bolton sees that moment , now iconic , as one more example of the fundamental thesis of his book .","depth":6},{"id":211,"text":"After the photo op , Defense Secretary Mark Esper and Gen. Mark Milley , chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff , said","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"they had been wrong","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"to participate in it ,","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"opening an extraordinary public divide between the president and the leaders of the nation 's military .","depth":8},{"id":215,"text":"`` Everything in the administration is at risk","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"of being torqued around Donald Trump 's personal needs , ''","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"Bolton told .","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"`` This happens over and over again , this fusing of legitimate government interests with Donald Trump 's personal interests . '","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"' He can stage any photo ops","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"he wants ,","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"Bolton says ,","depth":10},{"id":222,"text":"but `` if the president wants a photo op ,","depth":10},{"id":223,"text":"stand there by yourself . '","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"' If he had still been in the White House ,","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"would he have walked across the square with him ? `","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"` I have to say","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"in all honesty ,","depth":11},{"id":228,"text":"I probably would have , ''","depth":10},{"id":229,"text":"Bolton said .","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"It was the only moment","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"when he seemed rueful .","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"`` And I would have regretted it later . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":465,"left":0,"right":464,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":464,"left":431,"right":463,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":431,"left":371,"right":430,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":371,"left":265,"right":370,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":242,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":235,"right":241,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":1,"right":234,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":234,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":241,"left":240,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":4,"right":239,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":237,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":5,"right":236,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":236,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":248,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":11,"right":247,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":12,"right":246,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":246,"left":13,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":14,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":15,"right":243,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":263,"left":259,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":256,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":249,"right":255,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":249,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":252,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":20,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":250,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":24,"right":253,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":27,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"